    public class OpenSignin
extends org.apache.cocoon.generation.ServiceableGenerator
implements org.apache.avalon.framework.activity.Disposable
    A generator which implements sign in via OpenID. Requires JOpenId-1.08.jar from http://code.google.com/p/jopenid/ This file is based heavily on OpenIdServlet.java from the jopenid sample code.
    Version:
    0.8, 12/15/2012
    Author:
    Frank Smutniak, Center for Digital Research in the Humanities, http://cdrh.unl.edu
